id: MV00474240000010001Cloudy With a Chance of Meatballs 2
title: Cloudy With a Chance of Meatballs 2
description: His genius finally recognized by his idol Chester V, inventor Flint Lockwood (Bill Hader) gets to join Chester's company, where he can work full-time on technologies to help mankind. However, Flint soon discovers that his most-famous machine, which turns water into food, is still operating but now creates animal/vegetable hybrids. With the fate of humanity in Flint's hands, he and his friends set out to save the world from tacodiles, shrimpanzees and other deliciously dangerous creatures.
summary: Flint Lockwood learns that his most-famous invention is now creating animal/vegetable hybrids.
